 Purpose:
 Notes:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
        DEFINE VARIABLE cVariables  AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.
        DEFINE VARIABLE cResetGroup AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.
        DEFINE VARIABLE cName       AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.
        
        DEFINE BUFFER bttColumn FOR ttColumn.
        
